name: Chocobo to Mahou no Ehon: Majo to Shoujo to Go-nin no Yuusha
overview: Chocobo to Mahou no Ehon: Majo to Shoujo to Go-nin no Yuusha is an Adventure game, developed by h.a.n.d. Inc. and published by Square Enix, which was released in Japan in 2008.
